Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.19,0:00:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.62,0:00:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手帕拿了吗 卫生纸拿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.79,0:00:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 音姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.38,0:00:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以喝生水哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是去丛林探险
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修学旅行的目的地只是奈良罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.45,0:00:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到奈良 就是葛根粉条 奈良渍 柿叶寿司 鹿角
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 我倒是也没特别期待着啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就别用充满期待的表情说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.79,0:00:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托请别跟来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.67,0:00:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘带东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.63,0:00:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘带东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.36,0:00:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吊坠？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.10,0:00:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个 出行的护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:01:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保佑你不会遇到意外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以绝对不可以取下来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.76,0:01:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是爱操心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 音姐 昨晚我拜托的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同学的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.22,0:01:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.04,0:01:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 还有我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好照顾她的 请尽情去旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然令人期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱啊 恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远离学校 24小时一直待在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.28,0:03:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种机会不拿来和女孩子相好还能干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也不会做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是淡泊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔚蓝的大海 青涩的春天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涉君还是老样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总比把自己女朋友晾着不管的某人强多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 再这样说的话机会要溜走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让关系比现在更进一步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请加油吧 小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也会给你打气的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完后的便当盒 请分组收集
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你拿过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢慢享受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁边 空着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饱了就想睡觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然也有这个因素
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上音姐她说事前演讲什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忽然之间就翻开了历史教科书…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下面由义之来导游的话 就可以放心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑袋里已经什么都不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概小恋还比较熟悉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是你来给做我导游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好做导游的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是头一次两人出来旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.69,0:05:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起留下两人的珍贵回忆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 请问两位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 这不是新婚旅行而是修学旅行的讲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 人家胸卡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义之
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看 义之
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋 看起来很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 天枷也很喜欢动物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带她一起来的话一定会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看舞女姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞女姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是在京都吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我推荐的是入鹿的首冢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\pos(352,10)}苏我入鹿：日本飞鸟时代的中央豪族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以小看首冢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奈良的非官方指南上可是排首位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞女 头一次在首冢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 再摆开一点 那么再来4张…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 这深深的叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 因为没和义之君在一起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 小恋还是觉得混浴比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害羞 不要害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往的话这是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在交往的吧…我和义之
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有在期待着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩爱地牵着手漫步在奈良古都 来个充满爱意的约会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在耳边轻述你的美丽胜过那微笑的佛祖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夕阳下的展望台 深情一吻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本应该是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但涉和杉並以及我们全都是些电灯泡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.36,0:09:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人总找不到独自相处的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话当然会留下一声叹息了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 才不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修学旅行大家在一起是理所当然的 也很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且义之也和平常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想恋人应该是更加特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗得真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说 身体已经洗干净了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举行那例行的活动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去女生房间聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然要的就是这个 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和女孩子增进友谊的绝佳机会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总不能袖手旁观吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系 男生们一起热闹就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个爱情土豪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有你的话会我们会很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多说无益
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强行带走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是打扮好了就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生们的房 间 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想见面的话就去见面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说话的话就去说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踌躇不前是最不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今的少女所需要的是行动力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 准备和义之私通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私 私通？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对这种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多说无益
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强行带走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.31,0:11:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以让你们去男生房间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 这也算是救人一命的事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向得不到回报的恋人伸出爱的援手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学 学校里禁止不纯的异性交往
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月岛小姐 你的包裹送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义 义之？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙 来女生的房间…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.14,0:11:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 与其说是来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不请自来是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是乱来啊 涉那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说谁乱来？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是打击人啊 为你好才把你绑来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 月岛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.95,0:13:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那我们就将计就计 我们的房间就给你们两位慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你这不是给我们添乱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 会给其他人添麻烦的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 该吐槽的地方应该不是这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好机会 小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 难道说是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我和…义 义之两人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 现在才发觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为人家…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女澡堂中的各位有人丢失手机的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个服务员难道是μ型吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是老式旅馆 真是少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅馆工作很辛苦的 能派上用场的地方有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的好气氛给破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 和服挺合身的 也挺可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 要是我家也有个多好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开玩笑也别拿这事乱开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个不是挺快乐的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我鄙视你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.48,0:14:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻耶 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,μ这种机器人 要是没有就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用把话说到这份上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有 碍着你什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真对你的常识表示怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么这么讨厌μ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟μ有仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不关你什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的聚会搞僵了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那么生气真不一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法隆寺充满着圣德太子一族的怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\pos(352,10)}法隆寺：位于奈良县生驹郡班鸠町，圣德宗总寺院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说被施了咒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着像是打不开的门这类七大不可思议现象的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉並君 真是卖力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这算哪门子修学旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长这家伙 还对昨天的事耿耿于怀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义之 我们去看看佛祖大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来快来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面相好慈祥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛像一直被大家这么膜拜 敬奉着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样是人造出来的 为什么μ就不受欢迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想天枷同学的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以拥有自己的心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 义之 你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7万元
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是7万元啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:17:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这可不是随口开玩笑的吧 由梦这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿角真的打算要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 义之君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 奈奈佳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物买什么决定好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊 你可要好好听我诉苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要7万啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7万？ 什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角啊 鹿的角
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿角？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神来 小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也知道他少根筋 但没想到这么严重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩一天了 你得加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的 拿出点自信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天下午是最后的自由活动时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么地方想和义之一起去的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和义之…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算到了 累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上泡个澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义之
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能耽误些时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 关于明天下午的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由活动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.91,0:18:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是急死人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…明天你有什么安排吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.28,0:18:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概随便转转
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个超粗神经白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…有个地方想和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:18:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:18:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日大社
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\pos(352,10)}春日大社：位于奈良市春日野町，旧官币大社，日本三大神社之一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说那里供奉着结缘的神仙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结缘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有心型的图案
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把两个人的名字写在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 就可以和喜欢的人永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管到什么时候 不管发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人永不分离 恋人们恒久相依
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让恋爱顺利的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是和大家一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我和义之两个人一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 两个人一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们说好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义之君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊 一脸淫笑真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你明天去约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 为什么你会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.01,0:20:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们说好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.87,0:20:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 我的舞女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没抱过 没抱过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人羡慕死了 你这爱情土豪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:21:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不去泡澡了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去和音姐通个电话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗷 羡慕死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋 快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.83,0:21:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.83,0:21:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由梦吗 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你那边怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)}「喜欢你」「我爱你」「一辈子帮我洗内裤吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.77,0:23:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)}虽然有很多话可以传递心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.55,0:23:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)}但最重要的是一定要把心意传递给对方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)}不要以为这种话说不说对方都明白就…
